<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge. I have added some <b>information below about how our RAF scheme works</b> to help answer your query.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>Can I see the status of my referrals?</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">You will automatically receive email notifications when –</font></div><div style=""><ul><li><font face="arial">Any one you refer joins our RAF scheme</font></li><li><font face="arial">Any one you refer qualifies (this is the step when vouchers are sent)</font></li></ul></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Both of these emails provide a link where you can view your total referrals and qualified referrals.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Please note, <b>due to data protections regulations all data is anonymised</b>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>Why hasn’t my referral qualified yet?</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">There can be a delay between a referral joining the scheme and qualifying, this can be due to –</font></div><div style=""><ul><li><font face="arial">A gap between a referral receiving a quote and making a decision to purchase</font></li><li><font face="arial">A gap between the purchase and start date of a referral’s policy</font></li><li><font face="arial">The legal cooling-off period following the start date of an insurance policy&nbsp;</font></li></ul></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Hopefully, the above will help to answer your query. But if you have any further questions, please don't hesitate to get in touch.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>